snippet.title: Heat Wave Yurt Glamping
snippet.description:
I am in the US for a month having the adventure of my life. The only way to stay cool and go "camping" in Georgia was to rent an air conditioned Yurt. It was my first time in a Yurt and I put together a little video to show what that whole thing is all about. The state parks here rent these out and they come equipped with some basic stuff (beds, seating, lights). Bring your own bedding, food, and cooking supplies. It was a fun night hunkering down! 

The adventure will continue over the coming weeks. Stay tuned! 

Cheers everyone.

snippet.title: Working at a Campground - Nomad Job
snippet.description:
Day as a campground host in the remote Colorado Mountains.
Camp host at Himes Peak Campground in Meeker, Colorado.  
*My name is Brian.  I started living full time in a self built camper van in 2014 in my hometown of San Diego, CA.  I hit the road full-time in 2015 to pursue seasonal work and travel around the U.S.  I find free camping on public land and enjoy photography, hiking, biking, and kayaking in nature.  Join me on my adventures. 
Thanks for watching!

***Follow Your Dreams**

snippet.title: Inside The Budget Truck Home Of A Hustler!

Welcome back to another Liveration video! In this episode we speak to Steph, who chose alternative living from as soon as she could leave home, she shares her journey of how she came to be living in a box truck, as well all the other alternative ways she lived prior to that, including being horse drawn! 

Steph is crafty and thrifty, and therefore managed to convert her once empty box truck, in the cosy, unique, homely, creative home she has now, for only £500!!!! So DEFINITELY stick around for the full inside tour, as Steph demonstrates how you can keep costs as low as possible, and you wouldn't believe all the things she keeps in the van! it's not your usual fit out, that's for sure!....

snippet.title: She Custom Designed Her Gorgeous Tiny House w/ MASSIVE kitchen
snippet.description:
Her Links:
FREE GIFT! Juicy Love Bedroom Empowerment - http://eepurl.com/iL4tzA
Vixen Academy:  https://thevixenacademy.com/
LG Quiz: http://eepurl.com/hp6EkL
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@staceyvixenacademy/videos
Media/Press: https://thevixenacademy.com/staceymurphymedia/

Interested In Being Featured On The Channel? : http://bit.ly/Tour-Application

VIDEO DESCRIPTION:

Join Stacey as she takes viewers on a tour of her beautiful tiny home, the Tiny Vixen. Designed with women in mind, this home is vibrant, functional, and cozy, showcasing how tiny living can be both spacious and welcoming. If you're a woman considering tiny living, this tour is for you!

Vibrant Living Room for Connection and Community
When stepping into Stacey's living room, the first thing you'll notice is the vibrant art that brings the space to life. She designed this room to be a TV-free zone focused on connection and community. The seating area is perfect for putting on shoes or leaning against the credenza. This space is all about creating a welcoming atmosphere for friends and family.

Heart of the Home: The Kitchen
The kitchen is the heart of Stacey's tiny home, and it was essential to her to have a functional and beautiful space. She worked with her builder to create more counter space by relocating the refrigerator and adding open shelves. The kitchen features a gas cooktop, a deep sink, and a Panasonic 4-in-1 appliance that bakes, air fries, sautés, and pressure cooks. The kitchen is designed for both cooking and socializing, making it perfect for hosting.

Cozy and Functional Bathroom
Though it's the smallest room in the house, Stacey's bathroom packs a mighty punch. It features wallpaper for a pop of color and a rain shower for a luxurious feel. She also included a crystal and plants to enhance the energy of the space. The quartz countertop and gold accents make the bathroom feel like a spa.

Practical Laundry and Storage Solutions
In the hallway, Stacey opted for a washer and dryer instead of a linen closet, making it a practical choice for tiny living. The broom closet and pantry provide additional storage space. This setup ensures that every inch of space is used efficiently.

Meditation and Zen Space
Stacey's loft serves as a meditation room and office, divided by a bookshelf with plants. The serene environment is perfect for starting the day with meditation and capturing inspiration for her coaching and business. The space also includes a TV area with a pop of blue for relaxation.

Mystic Design Bedroom
The bedroom is Stacey's sanctuary with a Mystic design, featuring artwork that brings the space to life. The dresser bay and three shades of pink make the room feel larger and more inviting. The closet offers ample storage, and the step stool helps her reach everything. The double bed provides walking space and complements the aesthetic of the room.

Empowerment and Connection
Stacey believes in using her home as a 3D vision board to manifest love, health, and wealth. The Mystic design elements throughout the Tiny Vixen reflect this philosophy. She encourages viewers to explore their own Mystic design with the free Bedroom Empowerment gift linked in the description.

Join the Tiny Living Movement
Tiny living is becoming an essential solution to housing affordability. Stacey's journey from New York to Orlando and finally to California has shown her the transformative power of tiny living. She's passionate about advocating for this lifestyle and helping others find security and joy in tiny spaces.

Connect with Stacy
If you have questions about tiny living, design tips, or her cross-country journey, feel free to reach out to her at mysticddesignbystacey@gmail.com or visit her website at mysticddesignbystacey.com. Thank you for joining her on this tour of the Tiny Vixen!

snippet.title: DIY Bus Home Conversion - Small Home on Wheels
snippet.description:
Their Social Media Link:
Their Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/beduthebus/

Interested In Being Featured On The Channel? : http://bit.ly/Tour-Application

VIDEO DESCRIPTION:

Their only regret is not doing this sooner! Meet Bedu, the bus named after the Arabic word for desert nomad. As someone who is half-Egyptian, Moshera finds incorporating this name incredibly special. Alan and Moshera welcome viewers to Bedu the Bus for a full tour!

Functional Kitchen
Welcome to their kitchen! It's super functional, used multiple times a day for cooking. The layout is efficient, with everything organized around the stove. They have a convenient sink with a swivel faucet, a three-burner stove and oven combo, and a full-sized apartment fridge that stores up to two weeks' worth of food. The ample counter space is perfect for prepping, and their pantry and drawer storage keep everything tidy, including their cat food and supplies for their two pets.

Cozy Living Room
Their living room features a pull-out couch with plenty of storage underneath. It doubles as a guest bed. They also display postcards and photos from their travels. On the other side, they have a dining area and workspace. They rebuilt this section, adding storage for their hiking gear and outdoor equipment. Their tiny wood stove, tiled beautifully, heats the front of the bus, supplemented by a diesel heater in the back for extra warmth.

Bathroom & Closet Space
Their split bathroom setup includes a composting toilet and an Ikea cabinet and sink combo. The toilet plumbing keeps things simple, and the closet space here is perfect for bulkier clothing items and houses their electrical breaker box. Above, they have an AC unit powered by solar and a backup generator.

Shower Area
The shower area is functional with cedar planking to reduce mildew and a tub-style base. They mainly use it when hooked up to water and drainage facilities due to their smaller gray water tank.

Remote Work Life
When they first hit the road, both had remote jobs. Alan’s background is in human resources and corporate operations. Bus life has changed their perspective, pushing them towards financial independence and early retirement. Alan now runs an e-commerce shop called Drift Ways, selling Arab-themed merchandise, while Moshera works remotely in customer service for a software company.

Main Work Area
Originally designed for bunk beds, they converted this space into their main work area with a butcher block desktop. This area includes a nook for their cats and plenty of power, thanks to their 800 amp-hour lithium batteries and nearly 1500 watts of solar on the roof.

Bedroom Comfort
Their bedroom features a queen-sized bed with storage underneath for their battery bank, electrical system, and water tanks. They’ve added plenty of space for clothing and some cat-friendly features like stairs for their 20-year-old cat. It’s their favorite spot, equipped with a TV and video game console for relaxation.

Outdoor Storage & Roof Deck
They have outdoor storage boxes for gear and their propane system, which powers their oven and on-demand water heater. The roof deck is perfect for stargazing and additional storage.

Their only regret is not doing this sooner. The road is full of incredible sights and a supportive community. No matter your travel style, just go for it—the hardest part is deciding to start. Everything else will fall into place. Thanks for checking out their bus! Follow them on Instagram or TikTok at @BeduTheBus. Thanks so much!

snippet.title: Truck Bed FULL of Clothes from the Dumpster – We Found a Couple Things We Wanted!
snippet.description:
Hi hi and welcome to another dumpster diving adventure! We found SO many clothes today, the truck bed has never been so full of clothing haha! I have been wanting some new clothes and was going to go thrifting this week, but thankfully the dumpster provided several pieces that I will be keeping! We also found a pop filter which Alex has been wanting for his poetry readings – so today was a great day of saving money by finding things in the trash! I love when it works out like that :') 

As always, thank you so much for watching and I hope you have a wonderful day! Happy diving and movin' on!

Emergency Awesome New Videos https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

Covering Captain America 4 Brave New World Trailer Breakdown and Marvel Easter Eggs. Harrison Ford Thunderbolt Ross Red Hulk, Betty Ross returns from Incredible Hulk Movie and Edward Norton Hulk Easter Eggs. How Thunderbolt Ross becomes Red Hulk in the MCU. Thunderbolts Trailer. World War Hulk Movie Easter Eggs. The Leader from Incredible Hulk will be the main villain of Captain America 4 and how Thunderbolt Ross becomes US President after Secret Invasion.

Why Val wants Adamantium and Tiamat Celestial Body from The Eternals Ending. And how that sets up the Thunderbolts. And the Sentry Explained. Thunderbolts will be a direct continuation of the Captain America Brave New World Ending. It will also serve as an Avengers 5 Kang Dynasty Teaser for the New Avengers Team. Marvel MCU Reboot Plans Explained. What Happened to Marvel, Marvel Phase 4 post Avengers Endgame, Disney Plus Streaming problems, and Fixing Marvel.

Deadpool and Wolverine Trailer Connection. Wolverine vs Hulk, More Cameo Scenes, Sabretooth Returns, Wolverine vs Sabretooth. Deadpool vs Disney Jokes, Kevin Feige Marvel Jokes and 4th Wall Breaks. Why Marvel is rebooting the MCU, all the marvel movies and disney plus marvel tv shows with Avengers 6 Secret Wars. And what's going to change with all the Avengers, New Iron Man, X-Men Mutants like Wolverine, Deadpool, Fantastic Four, Ghost Rider, Spider-Man and other characters marvel previous had not been able to use the way they wanted in previous movies.

Deadpool 3 Trailer and other Cameo Scenes. Deadpool vs TVA Agents, Wolverine Yellow Suit. Fantastic Four Cameo Scenes and Connections. Original X-Men Return, Jean Grey Phoenix, Storm, Magneto, Professor X. House Of M Easter Eggs. Wolverine Variants, X-Men, X-Force Explained. How Deadpool 3 and Wolverine change the Fox Marvel Movies

Hugh Jackman Wolverine, MCU Wolverine Explained. Avengers 6 Secret Wars Teaser and the future of Wolverine and X-Men in the MCU. There will be more funny Deadpool vs Wolverine videos, Ryan Reynolds Hugh Jackman videos that they make in between movies

snippet.title: Saksi Express: July 12, 2024 [HD]
snippet.description:
Narito ang mga balitang ating sinaksihan ngayong Biyernes July 12, 2024.




- Bilyong pisong transaksyon sa mga bank account ni Guo mula noong 2019, nakuwestiyon kasunod ng freeze order


- La Niña alert, itinaas ng PAGASA


- DPWH: P240-B, nakalaan sa infrastructure projects para matugunan ang problema ng baha


- Oil price rollback, asahan sa susunod na linggo


- Senatorial Preferences Survey ng Pulse Asia para sa Eleksyon 2025


- Kapwa-akusado ni Pastor Apollo Quiboloy sa kasong human trafficking, nahuli


- Iba't ibang bansa at organisasyon, naghayag ng suporta sa arbitral award; China, umalma sa pahayag ng EU


- Japanese Ambassador to the Philippines Endo Kazuya, bumisita sa GMA Network


- Babaeng todo-kayod sa paglalakad para mag-deliver ng mga parcel, niregaluhan ng bisikleta ng isang netizen


- Lalaking dating tambay sa arcade, nagtapos na valedictorian ng kanilang batch sa kolehiyo


- K-Pop girl group na NewJeans, itinalagang honorary tourism ambassadors ng South Korea


- Direk Mark Reyes, nasa Japan para i-promote ang Voltes V The Ultraelectromagnetic version

snippet.title: 24 Oras Express: July 12, 2024 [HD]
snippet.description:
Narito ang mga maiinit na balita sa 24 Oras Express ngayong Biyernes, July 12, 2024.


- 2 patay nang manlaban umano sa mga maghahain ng warrant of arrest; 4 pulis, sugatan

- Isang kapwa-akusado ng pastor, arestado; DILG: nakatulong ang pabuya

- Freeze order vs. assets ni Guo at kaniya umanong mga kasosyo, inilabas ng CA

- Eroplano sa NAIA, lumampas sa rampa; 13 flights sa T3, na-delay

- Nationwide gun ban, ipatutupad sa July 22 (12:01am-11:59pm)

- Salpukan ng bus at pickup na ikinasawi ng 11 magkakaanak galing lamay, na-huli cam

- Amb. Endo: Phl at Japan, magtutulungan sa paghabol sa Japanese servicemen kung lumabag sa batas

- DFA: patuloy ang ugnayan sa pagitan ng PHL at China pero 'di papayag ang Phl na bawasan ang RORE missions

- Kapuso stars, excited na sa GMA Gala 2024; may patikim sa makakasama sa red carpet

- Lagay ng panahon ngayong weekend dahil sa habagat

- Barbie Forteza at David Licauco, masaya sa suportang natatanggap ng "That Kind of Love"

- Amorsolo painting, narekober; 2 suspek sa pagnanakaw, arestado

- Japanese Amb. to the PH Endo Kazuya, bumisita sa GMA Network

- Civil registrar na nakapirma sa mga peke umanong birth certificate, sinuspinde ng munisipyo

- Alok na discounted travel packages, dinagsa; DOT: tulong sa ekonomiya kung sa PHL papasyal

- Dennis matapos ang Tiktok hacking: "wala po akong anything vs. ABS-CBN, mataas po ang respeto ko sa kanila"

- Senatorial preferences survey ng Pulse Asia para sa eleksyon 2025

24 Oras is GMA Network’s flagship newscast, anchored by Mel Tiangco, Vicky Morales and Emil Sumangil. It airs on GMA-7 Mondays to Fridays at 6:30 PM (PHL Time) and on weekends at 5:30 PM. For more videos from 24 Oras, visit http://www.gmanews.tv/24oras.

snippet.title: Rico Blanco at Maris Racal, hiwalay na | ABS-CBN News
snippet.description:
Hiwalay na ang aktres na si Maris Racal at ang singer-composer na si Rico Blanco. 
Ito ang ipinagtapat ni Maris sa Star Magic Spotlight event nitong Biyernes, July 12. 
Hindi na idinetalye ng aktres ang dahilan ng paghihiwalay nila ni Rico, pero nilinaw rin niya na walang kinalaman ang on-screen partner niyang si Anthony Jennings sa hiwalayan. 
May 2021 nang isapubliko nina Rico at Maris ang kanilang relasyon.
